CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780665076
OL,3,CEx-officer says 'safety at risk' after
OL,4,Cshe was falsely linked to Henry Nowak
OL,6,FAnd his treatment by police has
OL,7,Fsparked a political row.
OL,9,FThe protest followed the sentencing of
OL,10,FVickrum Digwa, 23, to life
OL,11,Fimprisonment to serve a minimum of 21
OL,12,Fyears for the murder of 18-year-old Mr
OL,13,FNowak in December.
OL,15,FChristi Hill told us she found out she
OL,16,Fwas being falsely accused at around
OL,17,F3am on Tuesday when she was being sent
OL,18,Fa "barrage of screenshots and
OL,19,Fmessages."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
