OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780665076
OL,3,CEx-officer says 'safety at risk' after
OL,4,Cshe was falsely linked to Henry Nowak
OL,6,FShe said Hampshire Police contacted
OL,7,Fher to say she was being treated as a
OL,8,Fvictim due to what was happening
OL,9,Fonline and that they were monitoring
OL,10,Fthe situation.
OL,12,F"As the hours went by I think the
OL,13,Fgravity really hit about what was
OL,14,Fhappening, the speed that it was
OL,15,Fhappening.
OL,17,F"Just trying to get a gauge of where
OL,18,Fon earth this had come from, where it
OL,19,Fhad originated from, which was really
OL,20,Fhard to do when thousands are posting
OL,21,Fabout it."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780665076
OL,3,CEx-officer says 'safety at risk' after
OL,4,Cshe was falsely linked to Henry Nowak
OL,6,F"It was all over social media. So on
OL,7,FX, Instagram, TikTok, Facebook. All of
OL,8,Fthem had posts relating to it."
OL,10,F"There was quite a long period of time
OL,11,Fon Tuesday that people, users of X,
OL,12,Fwere using Grok to fact check whether
OL,13,FI was using my name and another name,
OL,14,Fwhether we were the arresting officers
OL,15,Fof Henry Nowak. To which Grok was
OL,16,Fquite confidently confirming yes they
OL,17,Fwere the people in the body worn video
OL,18,Fthat had been released, and they were
OL,19,Fthe arresting officers - which is
OL,20,Fsimply impossible for that to have
OL,21,Fhappened."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780665076
OL,3,CEx-officer says 'safety at risk' after
OL,4,Cshe was falsely linked to Henry Nowak
OL,6,FShe added that it's "really quite
OL,7,Fworrying that that false information
OL,8,Fwas being confirmed by Grok."
OL,10,FThe ex-officer said she then had to be
OL,11,Frelocated for her safety.
OL,13,F"I spoke with Hampshire Constabulary.
OL,14,FThey accepted the risk that was still
OL,15,Frising at the time that it wasn't
OL,16,Fappropriate for me to go home, so I'd
OL,17,Fbeen relocated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780665076
OL,3,CEx-officer says 'safety at risk' after
OL,4,Cshe was falsely linked to Henry Nowak
OL,6,F"I've still since not been able to go
OL,7,Fback to my home address as, you know,
OL,8,Fthere's still false information still
OL,9,Fcirculating online, putting my safety
OL,10,Fat risk which is not ideal as you can
OL,11,Fimagine.
OL,13,F"And it really has had an effect on
OL,14,Fall avenues of my life, let alone my
OL,15,Fsafety at the moment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780665076
OL,3,CEx-officer says 'safety at risk' after
OL,4,Cshe was falsely linked to Henry Nowak
OL,6,F"I must really just stress though,
OL,7,Fwhat's happened to me is awful. But
OL,8,Fwhat Henry Nowak's family are going
OL,9,Fthrough is an absolute travesty right
OL,10,Fnow. So I cannot compare that in any
OL,11,Fway shape of form and don't wish to."
OL,13,FThe former police constable added that
OL,14,Fthere she's frustrated that "what
OL,15,Fshould be a trusted source is
OL,16,Fconfirming such false information."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780665076
OL,3,CEx-officer says 'safety at risk' after
OL,4,Cshe was falsely linked to Henry Nowak
OL,6,F"I think it's quite shocking. You
OL,7,Fknow, people potentially trying to do
OL,8,Ftheir own due dilligence by using a
OL,9,Ftool that they trust that publishes
OL,10,Fonline. And as a tool it's let the
OL,11,Fwhole system down. I think it's been a
OL,12,Freal eye opener, it's the negative
OL,13,Feffect it can have if it's fuelling
OL,14,Fthis misinformation.
OL,16,F"What happened to Henry is a travesty
OL,17,Fand what the family don't need is
OL,18,Fanything else compounding what is
OL,19,Falready a really tough time."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780665076
OL,3,CEx-officer says 'safety at risk' after
OL,4,Cshe was falsely linked to Henry Nowak
OL,6,FChrist Hill told us she wouldn't want
OL,7,Fto see something like this happening
OL,8,Fagain, and would be interested in
OL,9,Fknowing what is going to be put in
OL,10,Fplace in the future to make sure this
OL,11,Fdoesn't happen again.
OL,13,FAnd she thinks that there has been a
OL,14,Flack of clear communications from
OL,15,FHampshire Constabulary to squash the
OL,16,Fmisinformation, which she says could
OL,17,Fhave happened a couple of days ago.
OL,19,FHampshire Constabulary and X have been
OL,20,Fapproached for comment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
